    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is offset by the high quantitative agreement across all QoIs and the conservative nature of the compression-bending loading scenario relative to clinical use. Re-validation against the February 2026 model revision using updated bench test data is planned for Q3 2026; the current package relies on the Q4 2025 experimental dataset collected under the prior model build.",
